snippet.title: Puzzle Quest 3 | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark on a heroic journey across Etheria to discover the meaning behind the ancient Red Dragon's dying words. Prepare for a new Quest!

This game is not yet rated.

Follow our quest to launch and get updates through all our official channels:
Official Site: www.PuzzleQuest3.com
Facebook: http://bit.ly/PuzzleQuest3FB
Twitter: https://twitter.com/puzzlequest3
Twitch: https://twitch.tv/infinityplustwo
